OL,6,FTwo years ago, 22-year-old Hannah
OL,7,FAitken died after buying poison online.
OL,9,FHannah's family believe she discovered
OL,10,Fthe substance on a so-called suicide
OL,11,Fforum, and they are now one of many
OL,12,Fbereaved families calling for a public
OL,13,Finquiry into the government's failure
OL,14,Fto prevent people being harmed in
OL,15,Fsimilar ways online.
OL,17,FThe substance that killed Hannah is
OL,18,Fthought to be responsible for more
OL,19,Fthan 130 deaths in the UK.
