OL,6,FHowever, it is still readily available
OL,7,Fonline, with pro-suicide forums
OL,8,Fguiding vulnerable people on its
OL,9,Fdeadly uses.
OL,11,FPete Aitken, Hannah's father, says
OL,12,Fthat what happened to his daughter
OL,13,Fcould happen to anyone.
OL,15,F"When you lose a daughter, a family
OL,16,Fmember like this, as a family you
OL,17,Fquestion yourself.
