OL,6,F"But then you meet other people, and
OL,7,Fyou soon realise we are all ordinary
OL,8,Fpeople. And yet that harm is out there
OL,9,Fwaiting to be found by teenagers."
OL,11,FA new report by suicide prevention
OL,12,Fcharity the Molly Rose Foundation
OL,13,Freveals three Government departments
OL,14,Freceived a total of sixty-five
OL,15,Fconcerns from coroners about the risks
OL,16,Fof further deaths from suicide forums
OL,17,Fand a single substance one promotes.
