OL,6,FAndy Burrows, Chief Executive of Molly
OL,7,FRose Foundation, said: "Nothing less
OL,8,Fthan a public inquiry is now needed to
OL,9,Flearn the countless lessons and act on
OL,10,Fthem to save lives."
OL,12,FResponding to the concerns raised in
OL,13,Fthe report, a Government spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "Suicide devastates families and
OL,15,Fwe are unequivocal about the
OL,16,Fresponsibilities online services have
OL,17,Fto keep people safe on their platforms.
