OL,6,F"The substance in question is closely
OL,7,Fmonitored and is reportable under the
OL,8,FPoisons Act, meaning retailers must
OL,9,Falert authorities if they suspect it
OL,10,Fis being bought to cause harm. We will
OL,11,Fcontinue to keep dangerous substances
OL,12,Funder review to ensure the right
OL,13,Fsafeguards are in place."
